divs: Sighting DetailsGents, on Tuesday December 18, 2012, at 6:00 Hour Local Time here in Venezuela, I took a picture with an iphone from the balcony of my apartment located on the east side of Caracas to the mountain Avila, then when we took a look to the picture, we realized that something appeared unexpectedly on the picture and it looks like an UFO (..??). (I am not a fanatic nor a UFO Hunter nor a Sky watcher), Though it seems to be an interesting issue. Thank you for your attention.
